      "description": "ESIMSubscription is a tool designed to help you manage your eSIM plans and subscription details.\nYou can easily record each eSIM’s name, carrier, country or region, plan cost, expiration date, QR code, and notes — all in one place. With built-in reminders, you’ll never miss a renewal or lose track of an active plan.\nThe app also supports multiple languages and home screen widgets, making it easy to check your current eSIMs at a glance.\nWhether you’re traveling abroad, working across borders, or managing multiple eSIMs long-term, eSIM Subscription helps you stay organized and keep every plan clearly under control.",
